'''Shalaman''' were a type of tree grown on [[Belsavis/Legends|Belsavis]] in orchards and used in furniture.<ref name="CotJ">[[Children of the Jedi (novel)|''Children of the Jedi'']]</ref> The [[Mluki]] government relied on [[R0/5T.N1 tree feeder]]s to maintain the shalaman orchards.<ref name="EGTD">''[[The Essential Guide to Droids]]''</ref>

